Class WebsocketTickerClient

java.lang.Object
com.binance4j.websocket.client.BaseWebsocketClient<Ticker>
com.binance4j.websocket.client.WebsocketTickerClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
WebsocketClient
public class WebsocketTickerClient extends BaseWebsocketClient<Ticker>
Handles 24hr rolling window ticker statistics for a single symbol. These are NOT the statistics of the UTC day, but a 24hr rolling window for the previous 24hrs.
